  "stem": "<p>Triangle <math><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi></math> is similar to triangle <math><mi>S</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>U</mi></math>, where vertices <math><mi>P</mi></math>, <math><mi>Q</mi></math>, <math><mi>R</mi></math> correspond to <math><mi>S</mi></math>, <math><mi>T</mi></math>, <math><mi>U</mi></math>, respectively. The length of each side of triangle <math><mi>S</mi><mi>T</mi><mi>U</mi></math> is <math><mn>5</mn></math> times the length of the corresponding side of triangle <math><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi><mi>R</mi></math>. If the length of side <math><mover><mrow><mi>P</mi><mi>Q</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math> is <math><mn>6</mn></math>, what is the length of side <math><mover><mrow><mi>S</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><mo>&#175;</mo></mover></math>?</p>",
