  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. Since corresponding sides of similar triangles are proportional and the scale factor from PQR to STU is 5, the length of ST is 5\u00b76 = 30.</p><p>Choice A adds 5 + 6. Choice C is 6/5. Choice D is 6\u00b76.</p>",
